messageBody:
Hi All,
 
I am working on development of Rational Rose Model which integrates testing functionalities of test class with the design class.
 
For this purpose, I am extending my test class from "TestBase" (which in turns extending "TestCase" in a different package junit.framework). The class TestBase implementing "TestClass" interface.
 
If anybody has done any work, in this field, please let me know, so I may be assured of following right track.
 
Thanks,
 
Pankaj
